Advisor: <a href="http://www.cs.princeton.edu/~appel/"> <b> Andrew Appel </b></a> <br>
Thesis: <b><cite><a href="/~sws/abstracts/lambda.shtml">The 
Apparent Link Between Typability and Computational Complexity in Lambda-Calculus</a></cite></b>
